  render_theorem(sec, "Pairwise Completeness Theorem (S963)", "All C(5,2) = 10 pairwise sums, 10 absolute differences, and 10 products of {D,K,E,b,L} are expressible as named constants or axiom-prime products. Zero accidental values among 30 operations.");
